---
title: North African Chicken Peanut Stew with Sweet Potatoes and Lime Yogurt
description: A creamy fiery North African spiced chicken stew with sweet potatoes and chilis will warm up the cold winter nights. A drizzle of lime yogurt helps cool the taste buds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/north-african-chicken-peanut-stew-cc632ae4.jpg
